This repository contains the NOVAK Protocol, associated standards (SP-1 through SP-8), 
technical manuals, diagrams, threat models (NTM-1 through NTM-3), cryptographic 
specifications (HVET, EIR, RGAC), Safety Gate (PL-X / PS-X), execution laws, 
and the full implementation reference.

